'''Wizard Akutha''' runs the [[Magic Guild Store - Runes and Staves|Rune Store]] in the [[Wizards' Guild]]. The [[quest]], [[The Hand in the Sand]], must be completed to access his store.

Due to the high price of his runes, it is not often worthwhile to buy from him. However, his shop does stock [[blood runes]] at the lowest price.

